org.eclipse.scada.vi.ui.draw2d

Class SymbolData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.scada.vi.ui.draw2d.SymbolData

  • public class SymbolData
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the data of the registered items for one symbol

    All items that are registered for one symbol will provide the data to the symbols SymbolData instance. The information can be accessed by calling methods like getPrimaryValue(String) or getValue(String).

    If the item was registered using SymbolContext.registerItem(String, String, String, boolean, boolean) with ignoreSummary set to true then the value of this dataitem will not be considered for the summary state.

    Since:
    0.17.0
